  "title": "Fitness Fusion Leader (Studio Manager) - Join Our Squad!",
  "description": "<p><em><strong>We're a vibrant fitness studio in Singapore blending workouts, community, and energy! We're looking for a buzzing Fitness Fusion Leader (Studio Manager) to lead our squad, inspire members, and drive the studio's vibe 💪</strong></em></p><p><strong>What You'll Do:</strong></p><ul><li>Lead studio operations, classes, and team of fit pros</li><li>Create epic member experiences & drive engagement</li><li>Collaborate on marketing, promotions, and growth</li><li>Manage schedules, bookings, and studio flow</li><li>Champion our fitness fusion culture!</li></ul><p><strong>Who We Want:</strong></p><ul><li>Passionate about fitness & leading teams</li><li>Energetic, empathetic, and loves connecting people</li><li>Organized with a knack for multitasking</li><li>Experience in fitness management/studio ops a plus!</li></ul><p><strong>Perks:</strong></p><ul><li>Competitive salary + performance incentives</li><li>Free studio access & classes for you!</li><li>Part of a buzzing fitness community</li><li>Growth opportunities in a cool studio 💥</li></ul><p><strong>Ready to Lead the Squad?</strong></p><p><em><strong>Apply now with your resume & tell us why you'd crush it as our Fitness Fusion Leader 😄</strong></em></p>",
